{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762172747362","path":null,"data":{"id":1621,"title":"Manulife:升級新產品之客戶推廣計劃及其他安排","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1676258573635,"tags":["宏利保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一、升級<span style=\"color: #169179;\">「財摯傳承保障計劃」及「財摯家傳保障計劃」(整付保費)</span>之客戶推廣計劃：</strong></span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">推廣期：2023年2月13日-2023年3月31日(包括首尾兩天)</span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">投保上述計劃，可享以下指定之保費折扣優惠</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-02-13/b626a7efd6654433b81d191864233c4a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、優化所有自願醫保認可產品「醫院」的釋義：</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A.涵蓋產品(所有宏利自願醫保認可產品之全新及現有保單)：</strong></span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">包括<strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\">宏利愛守護自願醫保標準計劃/宏利全護航自願醫保靈活計劃/宏利晉悅自願醫保靈活計劃</span></strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>B.生效日期：<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">2023年4月1日，</span></strong>不論該宏利自願醫保保單的保單生效日期或保單周年日為何日</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>C.保單條款更新：<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">2023年4月1日起，</span>「補充文件-香港公營醫院及私營醫院納入醫院的釋義」</strong>將會成為宏利自願醫保認可產品保單條款的一部分</span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">於保單下之保障並不會因該等更新而減少</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">所有宏利自願醫保認可產品的認可編號將不會因應該等更新被更改</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!--EndFragment--></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"NewsFlash-TC.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-02-13/d42dc2976f814b4da27dcac5cba22ea3.pdf","uploadTime":1676258203109,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"NewsFlash-EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-02-13/aca1a33ba04448d2946587fab80a1070.pdf","uploadTime":1676258206435,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"升級新產品之客戶推廣計劃.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-02-13/9f534af537664bafbf1821e10d01e7c0.pdf","uploadTime":1676258213290,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"MANULIFE","companyName":"宏利保險","productCodes":["MANULIFE:PSV","MANULIFE:PPS","MANULIFE:SVSP","MANULIFE:FVFP","MANULIFE:SVFP"],"productNames":["財摯傳承保障計劃","財摯家傳保障計劃","愛守護自願醫保標準計劃","全護航自願醫保靈活計劃","晉悅自願醫保靈活計劃"],"companyCodes":["MANULIFE"],"companyNames":["宏利保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1676255953518,"endEffectiveDate":1680230353537,"effective":false}}